### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get all attendances (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances

### Get attendances with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances?page=1&limit=5

### Create new attendance record
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "time": "08:30:00",
  "note": "On time arrival"
}

### Create attendance for another user
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "time": "09:15:00",
  "note": "Late arrival"
}

### Create attendance with early arrival
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-16",
  "time": "08:00:00",
  "note": "Early arrival"
}

### Get specific attendance by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/1

### Update attendance record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/attendances/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "note": "Updated: On time arrival - confirmed"
}

### Partial update attendance
PUT {{baseUrl}}/attendances/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "time": "09:00:00",
  "note": "Time corrected"
}

### Delete attendance record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/attendances/1

### Try to get deleted attendance (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/1